com.jgoodies.forms.builder

Interface FormBuilder.FormBuildingView

  • Enclosing class:
    FormBuilder

    public static interface FormBuilder.FormBuildingView
    Describes a view that can be integrated into an existing form using FormBuilder.add(FormBuildingView). It is intended to reduce the effort for embedding subpanels that are aligned with an outer layout context.

    Note: This is an experimental interface that is not yet part of the public FormBuilder API. It may change without further notice.
